title: United Kingdom Imports of Zinc & Related Articles
description: Imports of Zinc & Related Articles in the United Kingdom increased to 30.63 GBP Million in September from 15.26 GBP Million in August of 2022. Imports of Zinc & Related Articles in the United Kingdom averaged 16.45 GBP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 50.32 GBP Million in March of 2022 and a record low of 4.74 GBP Million in December of 2001. This page includes a chart with historical data for the United Kingdom Imports of Zinc & Related Articles.
author: Hm Customs And Excise
